# Age Group Spending Analysis

## Project Overview

This Python project performs data processing and visualization tasks on customer and purchase datasets. The primary goal is to understand the spending habits of different age groups. The project incorporates multiprocessing for efficient data transformation and generates relevant outputs in both CSV and PNG formats.

